562
00:41:08,250 --> 00:41:14,000
I can still beat you.

563
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:15,110
There.

564
00:41:15,110 --> 00:41:17,150
Are you sure?

565
00:41:17,150 --> 00:41:18,620
No regrets.

566
00:41:18,620 --> 00:41:21,830
You are as competitive as you were when you were young.

567
00:41:21,830 --> 00:41:24,040
I have a young attitude.

568
00:41:24,040 --> 00:41:25,940
Because of that,

569
00:41:25,940 --> 00:41:28,500
