570
00:41:28,500 --> 00:41:30,310
I'm not the one who's on medication every day.

571
00:41:30,310 --> 00:41:33,890
It's okay to be on medication. We are at that age.

572
00:41:33,890 --> 00:41:38,320
It's better than being muddle-headed. Being muddle-headed is not good.

573
00:41:44,080 --> 00:41:46,230
That's not fair, Old Tang.

574
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:49,250
Why chitchat when we're playing chess?

575
00:41:49,250 --> 00:41:50,640
